title: Dimitra Panteliadou
data: Dimitra Panteliadou is a Greek football striker currently playing in the Greek Championship for Aris Thessaloniki.[1][2] She is a member of the Greece national team, playing the 2004 Summer Olympics.[3] This biographical article related to women's association football in Greece is a stub.
